OL,5, Ikea has cut sick pay for unvaccinated 
OL,6, staff who need to self-isolate because 
OL,7, of Covid exposure and in some cases for
OL,8, workers who test positive.             
OL,10,FThe retail giant acknowledged it was an
OL,11,F"emotive topic" but said its policy had
OL,12,Fto evolve with changing circumstances. 
OL,14,FFrom this week, sick pay cuts will be  
OL,15,Fimplemented at Wessex Water and in the 
OL,16,FUS several major companies have started
OL,17,Fpenalising unjabbed workers.           
OL,19,FIt comes as firms struggle with mass   
OL,20,Fstaff absences and rising costs.       
